title: NFL ATL: Wild Card Weekend preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Wild Card Weekend preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling – get your 2014 started off the right way with a robust analysis of Wild Card Weekend.  Which teams will survive the first hurdle in the race toward Super Bowl XLVIII?  Listen in, join the conversation on Twitter using @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL and vote for the heroes in this year's Stitcher Awards at http://stitcher.promotw.com

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
